high_descs: Turn around and go to the round black table in the left corner.
Pick up the gray knife on the table.
Turn right and go to the small black table in the left corner across the kitchen.
Slice the tomato on top of the black table.
Turn right and go to the front of the white table on the left.
Place the gray knife in front of the salt shaker and on the left of the green sponge.
Go back to the small black table with the sliced tomato on top.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Turn right and go to the oven across the kitchen.
Place the tomato slice in the brown pan on the right back burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the tomato slice in it.
Turn around and go to the front of the white table on the right.
Place the pan with tomato in it on the right side of the bread towards the back of the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the pan on the stove with a slice of tomato to the table.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the round table.
Pick up the knife from the table, near the lamp.
Turn right, move to the shelf.
Slice the tomato on the shelf.
Turn right, move to the rectangle work table.
Put the knife on the table.
Turn left, move to the shelf.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the shelf.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Put the tomato slice in the pan on the right of the stove.
Pick up the pan on the right.
Turn left, move to the rectangle work table.
Put the pan on the table, on the right.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato slice into a pan, place the pan on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the dishwasher, then turn right again and head to the black table.
Pick up the knife on the far left.
Turn right and walk to the small black stand with food on it.
Use the knife to dice the tomato.
Turn around then go left to to the white table.
Put down the knife so it is standing up on the table
Go back to the small black stand.
Pick up the closest piece of diced tomato
Turn around, walk to the black table then turn left and go to the stove.
Put the tomato sliced in the bronze pan on the stove.
Pick up the bronze pan from the stove.
Turn around and go to the white table.
Place the bronze pan in the very upper right corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the bronze pan with a piece of diced tomato in it on the white table.
